</a> ，以及独唱者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shinee">SHINee</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/key">Key</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gi-dle">(G)I-DLE</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miyeon">Miyeon</a>和来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/got7">GOT7</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kim-yugyeom">Yugyeom</a> 。</p><p> 2024 年 KCON 德国的阵容、票务详情等尚未公布。密切关注此页面以获取最新更新。</p><h2> <strong>2024 年 KCON 德国的阵容如下：</strong></h2><p>追梦人<br /><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evnne">埃文尼</a><br />伊利特<br />乔1<br /><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kep1er">开普勒</a><br />钥匙<br />生命之吻<br />李英智<br />伦8<br />美妍<br />如今<br />ONF<br />瑞泽<br />男孩们<br />有谦</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="de" dir="ltr">[ <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/KCONGERMANY2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#KCONGERMANY2024</a> ] 第二阵容公布<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ILLIT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ILLIT</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/ILLIT_official?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@ILLIT_official</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/KEY?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#KEY</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/SHINee?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#SHINee</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/SHINee?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@SHINee</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/LUN8?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#LUN8</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/LUN8_official?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@LUN8_official</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MIYEON?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MIYEON</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GIDLE?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#GIDLE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/G_I_DLE?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@G_I_DLE</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NOWADAYS?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#NOWADAYS</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/CUBE_NOWADAYS?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@CUBE_NOWADAYS</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ONF?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ONF</a> <a href="https://t